In this life, we will suffer, just like Christ. He was tempted and tried, just like you and me. But many times, we don’t find our deepest calling or purpose without suffering along the way. Jesus is our model for both passion and compassion despite life's circumstances!

Growth can be painful. It means getting out of your comfort zone. It means getting inconvenienced. But if you don't grow, you don't change. And if you don't change, you stay stuck. Go through that pain to reap the reward!
